{"tid":2478774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"休班警唐建偉涉危駕撞斃電單車司機 死者遺產管理人興訟索償","createTime":"2021-04-07T10:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T10:35:54.000Z","uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8fc1f92f35e6513f5e74ee6b63663f06d2cf7d","tid":2478774,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"駐守新界南總區交通部的警員休班期間，在沙田大埔公路駕駛私家車時疑與電單車迎頭相撞，<span class=\"red\">任康文署救生員的電單車司機傷重死亡</span>。死者的遺產管理人入稟高等法院，向涉事休班交通警追討人身傷害賠償，惟入稟狀未交待索償額。<br />\n<br />\n原告為死者林日安的遺產管理人陳梅莉（譯音），被告為休班警唐建偉。案發於2018年4月3日，據報當日電單車於沙田大埔公路沙田嶺段遭私家車迎頭撞倒後，電單車司機林日安連人帶車飛向路邊鐵柱，倒地重創，送院後證實不治。駕駛私家車的被告事後被控以危險駕駛引致他人死亡罪。"},{"pid":"be8572df9a710dc687673ebf90e5570452594c3d","tid":2478774,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:02:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/HRN7SLS3OBDM7L7WKTMOW5P6VI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FHRN7SLS3OBDM7L7WKTMOW5P6VI%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=333bcef7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FHRN7SLS3OBDM7L7WKTMOW5P6VI%2F&h=c58abc34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/HRN7SLS3OBDM7L7WKTMOW5P6VI/</a>"},{"pid":"ca8da4eec6ca70cc26076f347c4dd7e07406badb","tid":2478774,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e83948593052da0196df3cdfb3ad49408ff86d4","tid":2478774,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"最後條党政權走狗比人判左坐幾耐"},{"pid":"d77f36be67e7a492b19e6773c3d7808656525ef0","tid":2478774,"uid":244332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0